    "description": "Pronounced 'cah-choh e pe-pe', we've given this speedy 'cheese and pepper' sauce an easy, indulgent upgrade. You'll add white cup mushrooms, melt in Italian cheese, and finish with truffle oil, before serving over spinach & ricotta ravioli.",
